    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Honest & Road-Ready \u2014 A Practical Fair Condition Value! This car is straightforward, dependable transportation that's ready to get you where you need to go! It does show its age with some visible wear on the exterior and interior \u2014 you'll notice the signs of everyday use \u2014 but mechanically it's holding its own and runs reliably. If you're looking for a no-nonsense vehicle that delivers solid value without the premium price tag, this one deserves a closer look. Come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
