      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Budget-Friendly & Honest \u2014 A Fixer or Basic Runner!** Looking for the most affordable way to get rolling? This vehicle is priced to reflect its condition \u2014 it has significant wear, some mechanical issues, and cosmetic imperfections that are visible. It's not a showroom star, but for a handy buyer, a second car, or someone on a tight budget, it could be just the ticket! Sold as-is, so come take a look and see if it fits your needs. No surprises \u2014 what you see is what you get!",
      "price": 4000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Reliable, well-maintained vehicle ready for its next adventure! This car drives smoothly and has been taken care of, offering a great balance of comfort and dependability. You'll notice some light signs of everyday use \u2014 minor cosmetic wear here and there \u2014 but nothing that affects performance or enjoyment. A solid choice for anyone wanting a quality ride without the mint-condition price tag!",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition \u2014 best suited for buyers on a tight budget who are comfortable with a project car or need basic transportation and can handle some repairs. The car does start and can be driven, but it has notable mechanical issues that will require attention, including rough idling, and the transmission may hesitate during shifts. Cosmetically, the exterior shows significant wear: the paint is faded and oxidized in multiple areas, there are visible dents and scratches on several panels, and some rust is present along the lower body. The interior is worn with torn upholstery, a cracked dashboard, and some non-functional features. We are pricing this vehicle honestly to reflect its true condition \u2014 it is not a daily driver for everyone, but for the right buyer willing to invest time and money into repairs, it can serve a purpose. Sold as-is with no warranty.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $34,000, a price that honestly reflects its good condition \u2014 and we want to be fully transparent about what that means before you consider purchasing. This car is in solid, dependable shape with clear signs of regular use and care. The exterior shows some minor wear consistent with everyday driving \u2014 think small surface scratches or light scuffs \u2014 but nothing that detracts significantly from its overall appearance. The interior is well-maintained with modest signs of use, such as slight wear on high-contact surfaces like the steering wheel and seat bolsters. Mechanically, this vehicle runs reliably and has been maintained adequately, though it is not without the typical minor imperfections you'd expect from a used car in this category. There are no major mechanical issues to disclose, but as with any pre-owned vehicle, we recommend a pre-purchase inspection by a trusted mechanic. Overall, this is a solid, honest buy for someone seeking a dependable daily driver at a fair price.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition \u2014 a high-mileage, well-worn car that requires significant attention before it can be considered reliable for regular use. The exterior shows substantial deterioration, including heavy paint fading, multiple dents, scratches, and possible surface rust in certain areas. The interior is noticeably worn, with damaged upholstery, cracked or broken trim pieces, and general signs of heavy use throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will require repair \u2014 expect to budget for meaningful work on drivetrain, suspension, or other systems. This vehicle is best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, someone looking for a project car, or a buyer who needs basic transportation and is comfortable with the risks involved. It is sold as-is, and a thorough pre-purchase inspection by a qualified mechanic is strongly recommended.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    }
